thread.title: BRIEF-Wuhu Shunrong Sanqi Interactive Entertainment Network Technology sees FY 2018 H1 net profit down 10.65 pct to up 1.11 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Wuhu Shunrong Sanqi Interactive Entertainment Network Technology sees FY 2018 H1 net profit down 10.65 pct to up 1.11 pct

organizations.name: wuhu shunrong sanqi interactive entertainment network technology co ltd
shunrong sanqi interactive entertainment network technology

text:
April 30(Reuters) - Wuhu Shunrong Sanqi Interactive Entertainment Network Technology Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2018 H1 net profit to decrease by 10.65 percent to increase by 1.11 percent, or to be 760 million yuan to 860 million yuan
* Says FY 2017 H1 net profit was 850.6 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/w3LCr9 Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
